			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>Been playing this while waiting for Guild Wars, and I thought some of you might be amused by one of the optional side quests. It's basically just a series of hidden collectibles, and when you find them all you get a prize. But the collectibles are garden gnomes with skulls for faces, and the reward is a pair of skulled garden gnome scythes. They have low damage and no stats, but a bonus effect that procs random effects on enemies during battle. Whenever they proc, they cackle like a tiny maniac.<br />
<br />
Can't find any good pictures or videos really, so these will have to do. The first shows what the gnome looks like, and the second shows the weapon (but sadly not the cackle).<br />
