			<title>Sleeping Dogs, crap on PC?</title>
			<link>http://www.graffe.com/forums/showthread.php?73976-Sleeping-Dogs-crap-on-PC&amp;goto=newpost</link>
			<pubDate>Fri, 17 Aug 2012 16:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
			<description><![CDATA[setting the visuals with High res tetures ot about medium for most things helped reduce terrible video lag (mostly it's the higher AA does the lag) 
Nvidia 450 card, game looks pretty good :) 
 
